# AG Safe Session (GSF-Investor)

**Full guide for agents:** [docs/operations/ag-safe-session-for-ag.md](docs/operations/ag-safe-session-for-ag.md)

## Automation (Cursor hooks)

- **sessionStart:** If no `.ag-session.json`, runs `npm run ag:session:start -- cursor-auto`.
- **beforeShellExecution:** Before prod Turso / `vercel deploy --prod`, runs `npm run ag:session:checkpoint` if not yet checkpointed.

## You must still know

| User says | You do |
|-----------|--------|
| 작업 시작 / 세션 시작 | Confirm hook ran start; read `ag:session:status` |
| 배포해줘 / prod seed | Hook runs checkpoint; then deploy/seed |
| 원상복구 / 롤백 | `npm run ag:session:rollback -- --all --dry-run` → user OK → `--yes` |
| 뭐가 바뀌었어? | `npm run ag:session:status` |

Never partial `git checkout origin/main -- files` for rollback. Never browser MCP for Vercel secrets.
